  <p class="text-static-page">
In the form of COOLTURE Concerts, in coordination with all the agents involved in the production of concerts, COOLTURE establishes a minimum budget for the confirmation of the event. The users make the purchase of the tickets prior to the production of the event for which they are offered with advantageous conditions.  </p>
  <p class="text-static-page">
When COOLTURE carries out the sale of all the locations offered for sale, the concert is confirmed and the sales section begins until the capacity of the selected establishment is completed.  </p>
  <p class="text-static-page">
