  <h2 class="title-text-static-page">Introduction</h2>
  <p class="text-static-page">
During the period that the state of alarm remains in force in Spain , that is, until the end of the period of validity of the last of the extensions of the state of alarm declared in Spain by virtue of the provisions of Royal Decree 463 / 2020, of March 14, declaring a state of alarm for the management of the health crisis situation caused by COVID-19 , COOLTURE in order to help establishments dedicated to providing hospitality services in Spain ( Hereinafter, the  Hotelier  or  Hoteliers ) will provide, through the Website, intermediation services between the Users and the Hoteliers, by virtue of which the Users may acquire certain bonuses offered by the Hoteliers , in Spain, that , subject to the general conditions set forth below and the particular conditions established by each of the Hoteliers, will allow Users to purchase certain products in the establishments open to the public owned by the Hoteliers, once the state of alarm ends (hereinafter, the  Intermediation Services in the Acquisition of Bonds ) .  </p>
  <p class="text-static-page">
In this Section of the General Conditions, the legal terms and conditions will be established that will regulate the provision of Intermediation Services in the Acquisition of Bonds . Without limiting the foregoing, in all matters not expressly regulated in this Section, shall apply the terms and conditions set out in Section II  Terms and conditions of the services offered through the Website .  </p>
  <p class="text-static-page">
For the purposes specified in these Terms and Conditions, the term  bond  or  Bonds  those document s , either n physical or electronic character, gained s through the Web site, which empowers n a l os User s to acquire a certain number of products in the establishment open to the public owned by the Hotelier , within a period of 6 months from the end of the state of alarm in Spain (hereinafter, the  Validity Period ).  </p>
  <h2 class="title-text-static-page">General Terms and Conditions applicable to Users</h2>
  <h2 class="title-text-static-page">2.1. Conditions of acquisition and exchange of the Bonds       </h2>
  <p class="text-static-page">
The Bonds may be acquired by the Users through the Website, however, since COOLTURE acts as a mere intermediary in the process of buying and selling the Bonds, each Bond may be used exclusively in establishments open to the public owned by the Hotelier who owns it. would have offered. For clarification purposes, the name and address of the establishment and / or establishments in which each Bonus may be exchanged will be included on the Website .  </p>
  <p class="text-static-page">
Users must be over 18 years of age in order to acquire Bonds that give them the right to consume alcoholic beverages. Notwithstanding the foregoing, the Hotelier will be responsible for verifying the age of the Users at the time the Bonus is exchanged.  </p>
  <p class="text-static-page">
Unless expressly provided otherwise, each Bonus may be redeemed exclusively once and may not be combined with other offers and / or gift vouchers . For clarification purposes, if for any reason the User will exchange the Bonus acquiring products offered by the Hotelier for a value less than the total value provided for in the Bonus, it will be understood that he has totally consumed the Bonus and no credit right will be born in favor of the User .  </p>
  <p class="text-static-page">
The Hoteliers may include additional conditions for the exchange of the Bonds, such as the possibility of exchanging them at a specific time or the exclusion of certain products or services generally offered to the public in the establishment , among others . Users must respect, in any case, the additional conditions provided by the Hoteliers.  </p>
  <p class="text-static-page">
